---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer id="acao" class="lf">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="lf-grid">
      <div class="lf-main">
        <p class="lf-label">VI · Ação</p>
        <h2 class="lf-title">
          Pronto para <span class="lf-italic signal-text">operar</span>.
        </h2>
        <p class="lf-sub">Escolha por onde começar.</p>

        <div class="lf-ctas">
          <a class="lf-cta lf-cta-primary" href="/diagnostico">
            <span class="lf-cta-label">Iniciar diagnóstico</span>
            <span class="lf-cta-arrow">→</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lf-cta lf-cta-secondary" href="/jo">
            <span class="lf-cta-label">Falar com o assistente</span>
            <span class="lf-cta-arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lf-blocks">
        <div class="lf-block">
          <p class="lf-block-label">Edição</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Edição I · MMXXVI</li>
            <li>Encontro de Labs</li>
            <li>Inovação pública</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lf-block">
          <p class="lf-block-label">Por</p>
          <ul>
            <li>CLIC</li>
            <li>Centro de letramento digital</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lf-block">
          <p class="lf-block-label">Construção coletiva</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a class="lf-block-link" href="/sugestoes?from=/">Como o Alavanca pode melhorar? →</a></li>
            <li>Plataforma aberta a contribuições.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lf-meta">
      <span>© CLIC · Alavanca · {year} · Inovação pública</span>
      <span class="lf-meta-edition">
        <span class="lf-meta-dot"></span> Edição I · MMXXVI
      </span>
      <span>BR · PT</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .lf {
    position: relative;
    padding: 128px 0 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }

  .lf-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .lf-main {
    grid-column: span 12;
  }
  @media (min-width: 880px) {
    .lf-main { grid-column: span 8; }
  }

  .lf-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-50);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .lf-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5.4rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--bone);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .lf-italic {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .lf-sub {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 36ch;
    color: var(--fg-65);
  }

  .lf-ctas {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .lf-ctas { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  }

  .lf-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    min-width: 280px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--bone);
    transition: background-color 250ms ease, border-color 250ms ease;
  }

  .lf-cta-primary {
    border: 1px solid var(--signal);
    background: oklch(0.82 0.155 78 / 0.10);
  }
  .lf-cta-primary:hover {
    background: oklch(0.82 0.155 78 / 0.18);
  }
  .lf-cta-primary .lf-cta-arrow { color: var(--signal); }

  .lf-cta-secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-30);
  }
  .lf-cta-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--signal);
    color: var(--signal);
  }

  .lf-cta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .lf-cta-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 20px;
    transition: transform 250ms ease;
  }
  .lf-cta:hover .lf-cta-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* ---------- BLOCKS ---------- */
  .lf-blocks {
    grid-column: span 12;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-self: end;
  }
  @media (min-width: 880px) {
    .lf-blocks { grid-column: span 4; }
  }

  .lf-block-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-50);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .lf-block ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--fg-65);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .lf-block-link {
    color: var(--fg-65);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 200ms ease;
  }
  .lf-block-link:hover {
    color: var(--signal);
  }

  /* ---------- META BAR ---------- */
  .lf-meta {
    margin-top: 96px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-50);
  }
  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .lf-meta {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  }

  .lf-meta-edition {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .lf-meta-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--signal);
    animation: blink 3.4s steps(1) infinite;
  }
</style>
